  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nPlease provide a brief description of the issue.\r\nIf you send post request with header `'Content-Type': 'application/json;charset=utf-8'` to endpoint /validator/subscribe it will return bad request error with message:\r\n> The provided content-type \"application/json;charset=utf-8\" is not available, this endpoint only supports json.\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nlatest docker\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nhttp error 400\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nhttp 200 OK\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nAccept charset in content-type header and respect it.",
